        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Dealt unfaithfully.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Turned away their faces from the habitation of the Lord.—Comp. Jeremiah 2:27 : “They have turned their backs unto me, and not their faces.” (Comp. also Ezekiel 8:16.)",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "Turned away their faces from the habitation of the Lord.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "—Comp. ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Jeremiah 2:27",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " : “They have turned their backs unto me, and not their faces.” (Comp. also ",
            "children": []
